WorkItem.Description: I get two different DPS calculations and two different gemming recommendations after running optimization. RAWR3 says I have 10k DPS and 2.3.17 says I have 12k DPS, not including pet. RAWR3 says I need to gem Haste gems and 2.3.17 says I need to gem Hit. WorkItem.Summary: RAWR3 BETA and 2.3.17 returning different DPS values/Gemming recommendations

Comments.Message: Rawr3 is currently equiavalent to 2.3.15.    I assume the differences are due to the version differences - assuming you have set every buff, talent, glyph and option in the options panel to exactly the same (and marked all the same enchants, gems & items as available)
